=====================
    VP4D_hybrid
=====================

Compilation
------------

mkdir build;
cd build;
ccmake ../src;
make;


To launch a simulation using SeLaLib solver
-------------------------------------------

cd ../wk;
mkdir run;
cd run;
mpirun -np 4 ../../build/bin/VP4D_hybrid.exe ../test_vp4D_anal_identity.txt > VP4D_res.out

(or any other test case that doesn't contain the word DJANGO in it.)


To launch a simulation using DJANGO solver
------------------------------------------

From the build:

export SLL_VP4D=$SLL_SIM_DIR/VP4D_hybrid
export SLL_PARAMDIR=$SLL_VP4D/wk/DJANGO_params
export SLL_GEOM=n_6464

poe $SLL_VP4D/build/bin/VP4D_hybrid.exe
$SLL_VP4D/wk/test_vp4D_anal_identity_DJANGO.txt  --django-params $SLL_PARAMDIR
--geometry $SLL_PARAMDIR/$SLL_GEOM


For visualization of results / diagnostics
------------------------------------------

python $SLL_SIMULATIONS_PATH/VP4D_hybrid/Python-scripts/VP4Dhyb_main.py
